info: This is a Johnson & Johnson mobile clinic being held at Capital Mall, 625 Black Lake Blvd SW, Olympia WA, 98502 for anyone age 18 and older from 12pm-8pm. info: ***We will accept both first and second dose appointments*** Insured, medicaid, medicare, and uninsured options all available.
